# Unzip, init repo, push
unzip session-mixer.zip
cd session-mixer
git init
git add .
git commit -m "init: SessionMix v2 — multi-app audio mixer"
git remote add origin git@github.com:YOUR_USERNAME/session-mixer.git
git push -u origin main

# Install and run
npm install
npm run dev
```

**Project structure at a glance:**
```
src/protocol.js   → Constants, message types, shared state
src/bridge.js     → The script injected into every app (AudioContext patching)
src/engine.js     → Transport clock, gain routing, meter ingestion
src/mixer.js      → Fader/pan/VU/solo/mute UI
src/channels.js   → Iframe loading, tab switching, CSS stacking
src/main.js       → Init, keyboard shortcuts, render loop
src/styles.css    → All styles
docs/SYNC-PROTOCOL.md → API spec for making your apps sync-ready
